SUMMARY:Deadline: Creative Industry Activities Programme Grant Scheme
DESCRIPTION:Multi-year grant for cultural institutions whose core task is t
 o contribute to the high quality\, development and professionalisation of 
 the contemporary creative industry through a two-year activities programme
 . Application window: 13 May 2026 15:00 CEST to 15 June 2026 16:00 CEST. M
 aximum requested amount €125\,000 per year\; total annual scheme budget 
 €1\,850\,000.\n\nOrganisation: Stimuleringsfonds Creatieve Industrie (Cr
 eative Industries Fund NL)\nLocation: Netherlands\nAward: Up to €125\,00
 0 per year per applicant (overall budget €1\,850\,000 per year)\nDuratio
 n: Two-year activities programme\n\nMore: https://www.stimuleringsfonds.nl
 /en/grants/creative-industry-activities-programme-grant-scheme
URL:https://www.stimuleringsfonds.nl/en/grants/creative-industry-activities
 -programme-grant-scheme
LOCATION:Netherlands
